1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:42,079
So? Any news?

3
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:43,359
Magistrate Yu went to the manor.

4
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,000
I also got this.

5
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:49,640
The layout of Wu Lian's room.

6
00:00:51,119 --> 00:00:52,640
The spots marked in red

7
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,560
are likely where he hides
the victim list.

8
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:56,000
This is Wu Lian's bedroom.

9
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,679
I've tried several times but failed.

10
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:00,039
So this must be telling us

11
00:01:00,039 --> 00:01:01,280
where the victim list is.

12
00:01:08,540 --> 00:01:12,460
=Episode 15=

13
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,480
Your Highness,

14
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,879
I have something to say.

15
00:01:14,879 --> 00:01:16,000
The evidence is right here.

16
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,239
How dare you lie?

17
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,280
Ruoheng!

18
00:01:19,239 --> 00:01:20,799
Magistrate Yu hasn't closed the case.

19
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,159
Don't be rude.

20
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:24,319
Even if he isn't the killer,

21
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:26,599
he failed to discipline his men.

22
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,359
Either way, he's involved.

23
00:01:28,519 --> 00:01:29,560
Exactly.

24
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:32,239
That's why I wanted to bring
Master Wu to the office.

25
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:35,359
The weapon was found in his bedroom.

26
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,640
So, who could freely

27
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,359
enter and exit his room?

28
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,719
Even if Master Wu isn't the killer,

29
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,640
then the killer

30
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:45,840
must be someone close to him.

31
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,079
Your Highness, please see the truth.

32
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,519
I've been embroidering your
gown every day.

33
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,200
Finding this object on me

34
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,760
only proves I've failed to supervise.

35
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,599
Murder is too heavy a charge.

36
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,879
I beg Magistrate Yu

37
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,959
to investigate thoroughly
before making decisions.

38
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:02,599
If a murder weapon can't prove guilt,

39
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,959
then how did Master Wu,

40
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:06,400
using just a hairpin,

41
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:08,479
send me to death row?

42
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:11,240
If Xiaotao hadn't risked
her life to save me,

43
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,680
I would already be dead

44
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:14,479
and unable to see the Prince

45
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:17,479
at the Flower Festival.

46
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,840
Your Highness,

47
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,919
the constables and officers

48
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:24,159
can all testify to how this was found.

49
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,840
I'm not lying.

50
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,439
Magistrate Yu,

51
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,879
those are serious words.

52
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:32,599
Did Lady Cheng'en promise you something

53
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,960
to make you spew such venom?

54
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:38,199
Wenyue,
you know I came to the manor alone.

55
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:39,919
My belongings haven't arrived.

56
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,800
What could I possibly
give Magistrate Yu?

57
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:45,599
Besides, after suffering in jail,

58
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:48,000
what favors would I have left?

59
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,240
Your Highness,

60
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:02,360
the one who gave me
the "Spring River" painting

61
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:06,360
was Meng Wan,
Wu Lian's head embroiderer.

62
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,879
So we caught her red-handed.

63
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,960
Meng Wan.

64
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,879
Behind my back,

65
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,680
you did such vile things.

66
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,319
Wenyue,

67
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,199
Wu Lian is blaming
others for his crimes.

68
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,319
In my view,

69
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:31,879
Ms. Meng is like a dog he keeps.

70
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,599
This painting is so precious.

71
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:36,360
How could a dog have stolen it?

72
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,039
Shut up!

73
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,080
In Her Highness's presence,

74
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:42,639
you have no right to speak.

75
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,639
Enough.

76
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,360
You're giving me a headache.

77
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:48,680
The Prince returns soon.

78
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:51,840
Do you want to ruin everything?

79
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,479
Magistrate Yu,

80
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:56,080
handle the case back at your office.

81
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:58,680
Report to me when you're done.

82
00:03:59,159 --> 00:03:59,719
Yes.

83
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:00,680
Your Highness,

84
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,840
one last thing.

85
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:03,840
Speak.

86
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,800
If I can prove

87
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,479
someone had free access
to my room,

88
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,000
framing me...

89
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,280
Any proof?

90
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:14,719
The manor checks the gown's
progress daily.

91
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:18,839
Each day, before the seal
is broken on the backing,

92
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,160
we stamp it with the
seal of the officer on duty.

93
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,680
Who can prove this?

94
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,480
Nanny Du.

95
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,240
Yes. Master Wu is right.

96
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,839
Magistrate Yu is smart.

97
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:52,160
He'll handle his case well.

98
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,959
But you two...

99
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:55,759
Wenyue,

100
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,720
I won't cause trouble anymore.

101
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,319
I'll follow your lead.

102
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:01,879
Your Highness,

103
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,759
I've given my all to the gown.

104
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,319
Failing to discipline my staff

105
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:06,480
is a fault.

106
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,879
But over the years,
what I've done for you...

107
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:09,680
Enough.

108
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,439
After all these years,

109
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:13,360
you don't need to say this.

110
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,160
Yes.

111
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,399
I'm not eloquent,

112
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:19,319
but my heart and hands
are truly sincere.

113
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,920
Like today.

114
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,759
I want you to do the
finishing touch.

115
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,839
This gown will speak for me.

116
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:30,560
(Jinxiu City's Yanyu Embroidery House)
No one else

117
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:34,040
can give you this noble,
magnificent beauty.

118
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,600
Nanny.

119
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,040
Master Wu.

120
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:08,319
Since the gown has been delivered,

121
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,600
why close the box?

122
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,399
There are foul rats in it.

123
00:06:14,399 --> 00:06:15,040
I fear...

124
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,759
I fear to startle Her Highness.

125
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,600
It doesn't matter. Open it.

126
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:43,439
A golden pheasant with its head raised

127
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,480
symbolizes your supreme status, Wenyue.

128
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,879
This Yanyu embroidery,

129
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,920
like mist and smoke,

130
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,879
truly lives up to its name.

131
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,560
Golden pheasant, head severed.

132
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,560
It's a bad omen.

133
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:04,720
Your Highness,

134
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,040
the break is rough.

135
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,439
It... it must have been
bitten by the rats.

136
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:17,460
(Inspect the back of
the pheasant's neck)

137
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,240
Your Highness, I failed to guard it.

138
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:21,360
I deserve to die.

139
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:24,680
Please allow me three more days.

140
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,800
In three days,

141
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,040
I'll make another.

142
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,800
I have given you many chances

143
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:31,199
because your heart is true
and your skill is fine.

144
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:33,040
Now, you show no respect.

145
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,240
Why should I forgive you?

146
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:39,800
Your Highness,

147
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,920
a delivery has arrived from
Cheng'en Manor.

148
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:44,759
(Cheng'en Manor sends
a gift at this moment?)

149
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:47,279
(Could there be a deeper meaning?)

150
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:50,639
(Ruoheng's delivery came
right on time.)

151
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:52,879
By custom,

152
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:56,360
you must receive Cheng'en Manor's
gift first

153
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,199
before dealing with this servant,
Your Highness.

154
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,560
All right.

155
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,800
Ruoheng,

156
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,279
come with me.

157
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,759
How's Xiaotao?

158
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:30,240
Still asleep.

159
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,960
So distracted.

160
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:40,080
Some people talk about staying calm,

161
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,360
but deep down,

162
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,559
they're the most anxious.

163
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:48,399
Mr. Liu, if all we can do is wait,

164
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:49,679
then why not be patient?

165
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,279
If we rush and make a mistake,

166
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,960
it would ruin Miss Rulan's

167
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,039
careful planning.

168
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,799
Rulan is facing danger alone,

169
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:59,639
taking the blame for all of us.

170
00:09:00,879 --> 00:09:02,039
And here I am, a grown man,

171
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,759
useless, just worrying.

172
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,159
Don't fret.

173
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,960
Lady Cheng'en's delivery
should have arrived.

174
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,639
It'll help Rulan.

175
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,240
Greetings, Your Highness.

176
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,799
How thoughtful of Cheng'en Manor.

177
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:23,399
I was ordered to deliver
newly made silk fabrics.

178
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:24,639
Please make your selection.

179
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:25,639
(Mr. Xiao, Attendant of Cheng'en Manor)
Here is the gift list.

180
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:27,060
(Mr. Xiao, Attendant of Cheng'en Manor)

181
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:29,879
Rise.

182
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:33,100
(Gift List)

183
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:37,799
Is this from Ruoheng?

184
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,559
Lady Cheng'en selected for you

185
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,840
fabrics favored by noblewomen

186
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,919
in the capital.

187
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,879
But the order took some time.

188
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:46,000
It couldn't arrive with
the first batch.

189
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,679
How thoughtful, Ruoheng.

190
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:54,960
(Why didn't this attendant)

191
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,200
(greeting Ruoheng, his master?)

192
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:59,679
(It's as if he doesn't recognize her.)

193
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:02,480
Your Highness,

194
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:05,799
they say after Lady Cheng'en arrived,

195
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,120
Lin Rulan's spirit entered her body

196
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,159
and took control.

197
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,080
Mr. Xiao,

198
00:10:12,799 --> 00:10:14,679
if you have a message for Lady Cheng'en,

199
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,720
deliver it to her directly.

200
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,759
(Oh no.)

201
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,639
(This attendant has never seen me.)

202
00:10:20,039 --> 00:10:21,480
(She noticed.)

203
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,320
There is indeed a personal letter
from Lord Cheng'en.

204
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,679
Your Highness,
please give it to Lady Cheng'en.

205
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,080
Mr. Xiao,

206
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,440
why not give it to her yourself?

207
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,360
Well...

208
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,159
Seeing you hesitate,

209
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:40,480
could it be
that you don't know Lady Cheng'en?

210
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,919
(I didn't expect)

211
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,440
(that he doesn't know Ruoheng.)

212
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:47,360
(What do I do now?)

213
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:20,860
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

214
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:24,100
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

215
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:28,060
♪The past no longer binds♪

216
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:32,260
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

217
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:36,820
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

218
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:40,540
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

219
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:42,900
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

220
00:11:42,900 --> 00:11:46,980
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

221
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,580
♪For your faith that never broke♪

222
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:53,900
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

223
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:56,700
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

224
00:11:56,700 --> 00:12:00,940
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

225
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:04,620
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

226
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:07,380
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

227
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:09,980
♪One thought turns into ash♪

228
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:16,300
♪No future left to write♪

229
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:19,180
♪If I never fall♪

230
00:12:19,220 --> 00:12:21,580
♪How could this waiting end♪

231
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:22,940
♪If I bear no scars♪

232
00:12:22,940 --> 00:12:25,260
♪How could I challenge fate♪

233
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:27,620
♪I knew there was no way back♪

234
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:31,620
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

235
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:33,860
♪For your faith that never broke♪

236
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:38,020
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

237
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:40,900
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

238
00:12:40,900 --> 00:12:45,300
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

239
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:48,980
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

240
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:51,580
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

241
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:53,940
♪One thought turns into ash♪

242
00:12:55,060 --> 00:13:00,300
♪No future left to write♪

243
00:13:01,180 --> 00:13:03,580
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

244
00:13:04,860 --> 00:13:06,980
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

245
00:13:08,660 --> 00:13:10,860
♪If we meet again someday♪

246
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:17,100
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
